## Key Discussion Points

### 1. WG Status and Draft Status
* **Presentation**: [01) Intro, WG Status, Draft Status](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-detnet-01-intro-wg-status-draft-status-02)
