## Next Steps
* **General Draft Coordination**: Authors of `draft-ietf-detnet-packet-timeslot-mechanism` and `draft-ietf-detnet-tcqf` will continue discussions on whether and how to merge their respective timeslot scheduling mechanisms.
* **Individual Submissions**: Authors of individual drafts (policing jitter control, traffic characteristic deviation, and PREOF OAM requirements) will refine their documents based on the session feedback, specifically regarding alignment with existing IEEE/ITU-T standards, the `detnet-yang` model, and generic DetNet OAM work.